name: "The Fields of Grey" by DeadPanZoom
description:
Emptiness across the fields,
The seeds thou sown shall bring thee yields.

All together small yet vast,
To plant the trees that ever last.

Some will come and some will go,
Stick to thy plan like RubenFro.

Many shall bow to defeats,
That's not the case with Michael Beets.

Cabline1 has just begun,
What she’s building is not yet done.

All together here and linked,
Connecting lines like Maxwell Inked.

Laurence Fuller knows the way,
To navigate "The Fields of Grey”.


"The Fields of Grey" project is a visual chronicle narration of a communities progression, but also one of personal growth and empowerment. "The Fields of Grey" leaves many open-ended interpretations up to the individual viewer.
